# рҹҡҖ Local Setup

## 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/pratheekr7777-dotcom/Tour-Management-System.git
```

## 2. Open in Eclipse

Import the project as an Existing Maven Project.

## 3. Configure PostgreSQL

Update your PostgreSQL connection details.

## 4. Build the Project

```bash
mvn clean install
```

## 5. Run on Apache Tomcat

Deploy the generated WAR file and open:

```text
http://localhost:8080/tour-management-system/home
```

---

# рҹҗі Docker Deployment

```bash
docker build -t tour-management-system .
docker run -p 8080:8080 tour-management-system
```

